headline: RFIL Shares Jump on Q4 Earnings Beat, Revenues Increase Y/Y
summary: RF Industries' stock jumps more than 21% in the premarket trading after Q4 earnings surpass estimates, with revenues rising 23% year over year and margins expanding sharply.
